title: Yeah It's That Bad - Complete Podcast Archive
description:
The complete archive of episodes, including After Dark and premium podcasts, for the now defunct comedy podcast, Yeah It's That Bad. The show reviews films with a score of 50% or less on Rotten Tomatoes and decide if it's truly as bad as people think.
